<i>adjective</i>: 괴롭다 [괴롭따/궤롭따] <i>noun</i>: 환난 [환ː난], 수난 [수난], 괴롬 [괴롬/궤롬], 괴로움 [괴로움/궤로움], 고행 [고행], 고난 [고난], 개고생 [개ː고생] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>괴롭다 [괴롭따/궤롭따]</dt><br>
<dd>suffering</dd><br>
<dd>몸이나 마음이 편하지 않고 아프고 고통스럽다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling pain in one's body or mind.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>환난 [환ː난]</dt><br>
<dd>hardship; adversity; ordeal; suffering</dd><br>
<dd>매우 걱정되고 고통스러운 일.</dd><br>
<dd>An extremely worrying and painful situation.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>수난 [수난]</dt><br>
<dd>1. suffering; ordeal</dd><br>
<dd>견디기 힘든 어려운 일을 당함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of suffering an unbearable experience.</dd><br>
<dd>2. Passion</dd><br>
<dd>기독교에서, 예수가 십자가에 못 박힐 때 당한 고난.</dd><br>
<dd>In Christianity, the suffering faced by Jesus Christ when he was crucified.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>괴롬 [괴롬/궤롬]</dt><br>
<dd>suffering; ordeal; agony</dd><br>
<dd>몸이나 마음이 고통스러운 상태. 또는 그런 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being in pain physically or emotionally, or this feeling.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>괴로움 [괴로움/궤로움]</dt><br>
<dd>suffering</dd><br>
<dd>몸이나 마음이 고통스러운 상태. 또는 그런 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>A state or feeling of pain in one's body or mind.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>고행 [고행]</dt><br>
<dd>1. penance; asceticism; mortification</dd><br>
<dd>불교에서, 몸으로 견디기 어려운 일들을 통하여 수행을 쌓는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>In Buddhism, an act of making oneself suffer physically, with an intention to suppress one's desire and find illumination.</dd><br>
<dd>2. suffering</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 힘들고 괴로운 일을 겪음.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) An act of going through a difficult and agonizing incident.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>고난 [고난]</dt><br>
<dd>hardship; trouble; suffering; difficulty; adversity; trial; ordeal</dd><br>
<dd>매우 괴롭고 어려움.</dd><br>
<dd>A state or situation which is extremely difficult and painful.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>개고생 [개ː고생]</dt><br>
<dd>hardship; trouble; suffering</dd><br>
<dd>아주 심하게 어렵고 힘든 일을 겪음.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of suffering from a very difficult and hard problem.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>